BALTRAD conda recipes
=====================

These recipes install baltrad into a <conda env>/baltrad/<module> path.

BALTRAD uses LD_LIBARY_PATH to specify the location of shared libraries.  
After installing the conda packages this variable will need to be set, for
example:

export LD_LIBRARY_PATH=/home/jhelmus/anaconda/envs/test_baltrad/baltrad/hlhdf/lib:/home/jhelmus/anaconda/envs/test_baltrad/baltrad/rave/lib:/home/jhelmus/anaconda/envs/test_baltrad/lib/
